 BY LINUS CHIBUIKE LAWMAKER representing Adamawa North Senatorial District in the 9th National Assembly, Senator Elisha Abbo, has dumped the Peoples Democratic Party for the All Progressives Congress. Senate President Ahmad Lawan read the senator’s defection letter during plenary on Wednesday. Abbo hinged his decision on what he called mismanagement of the PDP in Adamawa State. Details later…  